'The Dead walk amongst the trees! Ethring is a small village without skilled warriors to take on these supernatural forces. 

'Perhaps you can defeat these ruthless souls and help us secure the safety of this town.'

<rgb=#FF0000>This bounty can only be completed a maximum of three times.</rgb>
Defeated Ruthless Dead in Ringló Vale.
You have defeated many Ruthless Dead in Ringló Vale and the people of Ethring are grateful for your deeds.
The village of Ethring hopes to thwart plans of the Ruthless Dead in the the Vale by defeating any forces patrolling the valley.
Ruthless dead can be found throughout Ringló Vale.\n\nDefeat Ruthless Dead in Ringló Vale.
